{"tid":1960258,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[立場] 張建宗：充分肯定警隊助截斷病毒傳播鏈的努力","createTime":"2020-04-06T04:55:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-06T05:14:02.000Z","uid":126889,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7a1a5c3abcec09a3207ee35cc27023eca4d56ed6","tid":1960258,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T04:55:02.000Z","msg":"政務司司長張建宗在網誌表示，上星期去警察總部，了解警隊協助新型肺炎患者接觸者追蹤的工作，指警隊以超級電腦分析，「充分發揮其刑偵的技能」，在協助截斷病毒傳播鏈作出的努力，值得充分肯定。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗指，警方調查多宗本地感染案件，如西灣河群組、北角福慧精舍群組，以及蘭桂坊小型本地爆發，並追尋多名確診的士司機的乘客和多名曾接載確診者的的士司機。另外又鎖定一些傳播熱點，群組源頭和超級傳播者，將資料交予衞生署跟進，以盡快阻止疫情在社區擴散。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>發 5.1 萬強制檢疫令 80 人涉違例<br />\n</strong><br />\n他又指，自3月19日至3月31日，政府向海外來港人士發出超過5.1萬張強制檢疫令，合共有約80人涉嫌違例。另外，三人早前違反強制居家檢疫令被檢控，並被判處即時監禁。他說不能單靠執法和檢控來防止病毒在社區傳播，市民自律守法才是成功防疫抗疫的關鍵因素。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>增建檢疫單位</strong><br />\n<br />\n張建宗又指，隨著疫情迅速發展，檢疫設施的需求大為增加，政府正趕緊翻修和加建工程，增建檢疫單位。三月中旬起，已預備於駿洋邨第三及第四座增加更多檢疫單位，目標是在本月內增加約1,660個單位。另外，會繼續在柴灣鯉魚門公園及度假村、西貢戶外康樂中心、少訊中心和位於竹篙灣的政府土地，透過組裝合成建築方法合共增建至少約1 000個單位的檢疫設施，預計可於四至七月份分階段完成及投入使用。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 未來真係刺激"},{"pid":"b505a6996fda4ecee4bd5ac7fcab8f4a2b9484b9","tid":1960258,"uid":55851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T04:56:38.000Z","msg":"曲緊喎，明顯寸鳩黑警冇做野啦<br />\n牙宗又撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93935cfc8553650b0549394d27bd62b151a59de9","tid":1960258,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b505a6996fda4ecee4bd5ac7fcab8f4a2b9484b9","tid":1960258,"uid":55851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T04:56:38.000Z","msg":"曲緊喎，明顯寸鳩黑警冇做野啦<br />\n牙宗又撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T05:01:11.000Z","msg":"你點解讀到牙宗撚狗?"},{"pid":"30be160cb29927dc3451bd603f35b2d3fc00d607","tid":1960258,"uid":119232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T05:02:38.000Z","msg":"重點係超級電腦"},{"pid":"0e9593f5741f66aca199bcb3015e2975ab89ccd0","tid":1960258,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30be160cb29927dc3451bd603f35b2d3fc00d607","tid":1960258,"uid":119232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T05:02:38.000Z","msg":"重點係超級電腦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T05:04:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">指警隊以超級電腦分析</span><br />\n<br />\n又想拎錢 成班宇宙殘渣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a16ce6597744b3847f05450f59a86109297040b","tid":1960258,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e9593f5741f66aca199bcb3015e2975ab89ccd0","tid":1960258,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30be160cb29927dc3451bd603f35b2d3fc00d607","tid":1960258,"uid":119232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T05:02:38.000Z","msg":"重點係超級電腦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T05:04:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">指警隊以超級電腦分析</span><br />\n<br />\n又想拎錢 成班宇宙殘渣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T05:05:50.000Z","msg":"仲有無限擴張權力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一齊抗疫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n警察都學識醫埋人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4252b9197dc11be7aec4865a746d89aa772cc3eb","tid":1960258,"uid":178078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-